{"tid":1721024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"次撚次贏得開撚晒巷連登就吹起一陣失敗風","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:59:59.000Z","uid":55739,"like":119,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"35a422448dceedb3d67311812c691ec37edb6d1f","tid":1721024,"uid":55739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"痴撚晒線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中大到打撚到64咁大把人睇完由藍變黃<br />\n身邊幾個朋友啲老豆老母睇完都變做黃<br />\n有啲之前藍既比人塞左2日都唔屌<br />\n無論朝早定夜晚都有手足打<br />\n打撚到班狗連放工嘅時間都冇<br />\n人權法今日放風大捷<br />\n英國第一次提人權法<br />\n<br />\n今日只係塞效果冇前2日咁好<br />\n之後有班撚樣出黎吹風<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">]仆街啦政府冷處理啦<br />\n人民鬥人民啦 <br />\n冇晒方向</span><br />\n<br />\n點撚樣冷處理啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知唔知塞撚到咁好撚多公司嘅活動都會取消晒<br />\n咁撚樣攬炒政府都可以冷處理未攬炒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實今日已經係<br />\n大西北 東鐵線大圍打後打撚把人番唔到工<br />\n課又停撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你仲想點撚樣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出面仲打緊啊<br />\n甘得閒上黎吹風<br />\n不如你：<br />\n1.做和理非應該做的事<br />\n2.出去幫手<br />\n3.早啲訓聽日去Suck"},{"pid":"6a8cb2d6fb1913757775d8c87d24f131ec82f605","tid":1721024,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:11:12.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b386aae778bb5b675d8dd6998b709e98ef4cdd7a","tid":1721024,"uid":55739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35a422448dceedb3d67311812c691ec37edb6d1f","tid":1721024,"uid":55739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"痴撚晒線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中大到打撚到64咁大把人睇完由藍變黃<br />\n身邊幾個朋友啲老豆老母睇完都變做黃<br />\n有啲之前藍既比人塞左2日都唔屌<br />\n無論朝早定夜晚都有手足打<br />\n打撚到班狗連放工嘅時間都冇<br />\n人權法今日放風大捷<br />\n英國第一次提人權法<br />\n<br />\n今日只係塞效果冇前2日咁好<br />\n之後有班撚樣出黎吹風<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">]仆街啦政府冷處理啦<br />\n人民鬥人民啦 <br />\n冇晒方向</span><br />\n<br />\n點撚樣冷處理啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知唔知塞撚到咁好撚多公司嘅活動都會取消晒<br />\n咁撚樣攬炒政府都可以冷處理未攬炒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實今日已經係<br />\n大西北 東鐵線大圍打後打撚把人番唔到工<br />\n課又停撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你仲想點撚樣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出面仲打緊啊<br />\n甘得閒上黎吹風<br />\n不如你：<br />\n1.做和理非應該做的事<br />\n2.出去幫手<br />\n3.早啲訓聽日去Suck"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:11:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af497ebc07de101500bd42fa5d0334efe6dec865","tid":1721024,"uid":55739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:11:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a57b94d94d1563aa5027b8fe6cc20709a9d90052","tid":1721024,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:11:49.000Z","msg":"正確心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbeac6568c7caefa38a7a089415164b1baf78e3f","tid":1721024,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86df9b65549a54ca95f22084b68c9fc1a96c19e9","tid":1721024,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"次次都係咁<br />\n<br />\n敵人永遠同一招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b38e169d212cce5c96ad21606267fc62af2873d","tid":1721024,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:12:11.000Z","msg":"係咁 仲有休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo